Image Prompt:
Create an ethereal and luminous depiction of Jesus Christ walking on water at night, with moonlight gently illuminating the calm waters beneath his feet. His compassionate gaze is directed towards a small boat filled with his disciples who are in awe of this miraculous sight. The serene scene captures the divine presence and power of Christ as he demonstrates his ability to defy the laws of nature, symbolizing faith, protection, and guidance in times of uncertainty.
